result.name: Zushi ANA

reviews.text: Great place with amazing staff. We had made a last minute reservation at this place from our hotel, but arrived late and at closing time. However the staff let us sit down and have a meal. We did have to order everything in one go because the kitchen was closing. Everyone there was extremely nice and the food was great. Their matcha rice cakes with red bean are amazing.
The chirashizushi lunch set is good value.  Fresh ingredients and delicious with nice portions.
Japanese restaurant serving different kinds of Japanese cuisine, sushi, sashimi, fried food and etc. The food taste good, the price was a bit expensive, but reasonable
Menu with good variety though food is not really authentic Japanese cuisine.

Fact...sushi in hong kong is expensive. Keeping that in mind, the quality and portion here is adequate. The service is good and quick. Lunch time rush here can be very busy. There is a large variety of choice from sushi to actual cooked bowls. The sets come with a couple appetizers and also a dessert. It is expensive to come here often but the food itself is good and flavourful.

result.name: 鮨穴

reviews.text:
2019 5月
女侍應比男侍應招呼好。

2019 4月
有驚喜的日本料理餐廳！
地方大，座位闊。
天婦羅，味道及口感比外表好，以價論質，超班。
沙律可以，吉列豬多了點油。
甜品好食，口感特別，應該係自家制。
有下次！👍🏻✨✨✨✨
食品 Food/Drink: 4/5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
價格 Price: 4/5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
服務 Service: 4/5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
環境 Environment: 4/5 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️

カウンターに鮨コーナーがあるものの、メニューは鮨の他、焼き物、串物、天ぷら、一品料理等あり、むしろ居酒屋の雰囲気。しかし、鮨もそれなりに旨く、他の料理も及第点。一品100~300HKDなのでこれくらいは普通と思う/ Though there's $ushi counter table, there are choice of 'roasted'' 'Skewers', 'Tenpura' and a-la-carte. Then it's more alike Izakaya style. But sushi is good and other dishes are also tasty enough. For a plate, the price is btw 100-300HKD so it's average.

Great place with amazing staff. We had made a last minute reservation at this place from our hotel, but arrived late and at closing time. However the staff let us sit down and have a meal. We did have to order everything in one go because the kitchen was closing. Everyone there was extremely nice and the food was great. Their matcha rice cakes with red bean are amazing.
The chirashizushi lunch set is good value.  Fresh ingredients and delicious with nice portions.
Japanese restaurant serving different kinds of Japanese cuisine, sushi, sashimi, fried food and etc. The food taste good, the price was a bit expensive, but reasonable
